/*  Utility . . . : STRPREPRC                                          */                      
/*  Object  . . . : A_INSTALL  (PGM)                                   */                      
/*  Source member : A_INSTALL                                          */                      
/*  Source type . : CLLE                                               */                      
/*  Description   : STRPREPRC - Installer                              */                      
